%% Data Flow Template
%% Traces a request from user input through all layers and back.
%% Replace placeholder names with actual components.

flowchart LR
    User([User]) --> Form[Form Input]
    Form --> Validation{Client Validation}
    Validation -->|Valid| HTTP[HTTP Request]
    Validation -->|Invalid| ErrorUI[Error Display]

    HTTP --> Interceptor[Auth Interceptor]
    Interceptor --> Controller[REST Controller]
    Controller --> Service[Service Layer]
    Service --> Rules{Business Rules}
    Rules -->|Pass| Repository[Repository]
    Rules -->|Fail| ErrorResponse[Error Response]
    Repository --> DB[(Database)]

    DB --> Repository
    Repository --> Service
    Service --> Controller
    Controller --> HTTP
    HTTP --> UI[UI Update]
    ErrorResponse --> HTTP
